00:00:01,202 --> 00:00:02,436
Previously on Lucifer...

2
00:00:02,470 --> 00:00:04,138
We need to figure out
who kidnapped me.

3
00:00:04,172 --> 00:00:05,739
I'm fairly certain that
my Father's behind it.

4
00:00:05,773 --> 00:00:06,807
AMENADIEL: Lucifer,
I'm not angry with you,

5
00:00:06,840 --> 00:00:07,841
that you somehow
got your wings back,

6
00:00:07,875 --> 00:00:10,578
or even that
you cut them off again.

7
00:00:10,611 --> 00:00:12,413
I was tested once,
and I failed.

8
00:00:12,446 --> 00:00:13,614
I'm not gonna fail again.

9
00:00:13,647 --> 00:00:16,016
I suppose this won't bother you.

10
00:00:16,650 --> 00:00:17,618
But you cut them off.

11
00:00:17,651 --> 00:00:18,752
The pesky things seem to be

12
00:00:18,786 --> 00:00:20,654
a bit more tenacious
this time around.

13
00:00:20,688 --> 00:00:22,156
I'm Lieutenant Marcus Pierce.

14
00:00:22,190 --> 00:00:23,624
DAN: Heard a lot about
you, Lieutenant,

15
00:00:23,657 --> 00:00:25,226
and I'm really excited
to work with you.

16
00:00:25,259 --> 00:00:27,095
Aren't you that corrupt
cop that got off easy?

17
00:00:27,128 --> 00:00:27,961
Excuse me?

18
00:00:27,995 --> 00:00:28,929
People come to me
to ask for favors,

19
00:00:28,962 --> 00:00:31,165
and more often than not,
I'm happy to oblige.

20
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:32,300
What do you get?

21
00:00:32,333 --> 00:00:34,568
Simply to be repaid
at a later date.

22
00:00:34,602 --> 00:00:37,405
A devilish IOU, if you will.

23
00:00:37,438 --> 00:00:39,573
LUCIFER:
Who's the Sinnerman?

24
00:00:39,607 --> 00:00:41,175
That's who hired me
to kidnap you.

25
00:00:41,209 --> 00:00:43,511
He's a scary dude.
Huge crime boss.

26
00:00:43,544 --> 00:00:44,645
And where do I find him?

27
